&lt;p&gt;Hywel Dda University Health Board are looking to recruit an Advanced Nurse Practitioner to join our managed practice Ashgrove Medical Centre in Llanelli.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a passionate and thoughtful Practitioner looking to join the local NHS Health Board and make a contribution to our forward thinking teams? We are able to offer flexible working to help support your work/life balance with access to professional and personal development opportunities and support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 25th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
